{"tid":2146574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"庫爾德建國夢 : 我們都想有個自由的國家","createTime":"2020-08-08T16:25:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T15:33:52.000Z","uid":314244,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e013761ee6964a60afbeb2b0499e2d992fc5045b","tid":2146574,"uid":314244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T16:25:01.000Z","msg":"庫爾德人為世上規模最大的無獨立國家民族，生活在土耳其、伊拉克、敘利亞和亞美尼亞交界的山區，人口在2,500萬到3,500萬之間。一二戰後各地民族主義興起，庫爾德人屢次有機會圓夢，卻被四國打壓屠殺。<br />\n佢地甚至成立左自己嘅民兵（佩什梅格，Peshmerga）保護庫爾德人同對抗ISIS。2015年1月，成功攻克ISIS係敘利亞的大本營科巴尼。<br />\n<br />\n以下呢段片都幾值得睇：<br />\n<br />\n庫爾德戰士憶駁火場面嘆香港如中東戰場：警察怎能把市民當恐怖分子？（果籽）<br />\n<ins><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9LPxj0ID4vM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9LPxj0ID4vM&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW5nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=7be5c7c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9LPxj0ID4vM</a></ins><br />\n<br />\n中東變局：關於庫爾德人 你需知道的幾件事<br />\n<ins><a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-50060829\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-50060829&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW5nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=1d1962ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-50060829&h=9a168cc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-50060829</a></ins>"},{"pid":"3121d4e0cd52512d6ebbb7ec251664b036bab543","tid":2146574,"uid":307927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T16:39:30.000Z","msg":"勁多靚女"},{"pid":"0fe44928a381fcd5ba2a16d51842bb9e74fd8177","tid":2146574,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T16:43:33.000Z","msg":"好慘！被Trump 拋棄，其實我希望trump贏，但會懷疑trump會唔會對香港人好似庫爾德人咁"},{"pid":"02b8260f7060bb5ed0000231b80827a3b917570a","tid":2146574,"uid":124113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T16:44:22.000Z","msg":"蘋果記者<img sr